dct_title_s: Map of the lower portion Muskingum River Basin and adjacent Ohio River Tributaries showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Lower portion of the Muskingum River Basin and adjacent Ohio River Tributaries
dct_description_sm: Scale bar lower left corner of map.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the lower Muskingum and Little Hocking River Basins and quality of underground water.
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water"
